        "username": "lba1_2",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/lba1_2/{size}/411_2.png",
        "created_at": "2006-12-17T11:38:56.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Hello everyone,</p>\n<p>i am quite knew here (look at my posts!) <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/smiley.png?v=12\" title=\":smiley:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":smiley:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<p>Anyway i read about being able to change your charecter and be some one else e.g Zoe</p>\n<p>but i could never work out how to do it?? Could someone please tell me anything about it.</p>\n<p>thanks in advance. <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>",
