        "cooked": "<p>Thankyou for replying <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/smiley.png?v=12\" title=\":smiley:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":smiley:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<p>Last night i was doing the same thing but with anim.HQR but i did not know you had to edit Body.HQR to make the charecters diferent.</p>\n<p>Edit:</p>\n<p>WOW!! i just tried it. Cool im the tralu !!!</p>\n<p>Thanks!!</p>",
